OL,3,CGloucestershire Chief Constable
OL,4,Csuspended following alleged misconduct
OL,6,FThe Chief Constable of Gloucestershire
OL,7,FPolice, Rod Hansen, has been suspended
OL,8,Ffollowing an alleged breach of
OL,9,Fstandards of professional behaviour.
OL,11,FHis suspension has been confirmed by
OL,12,Fthe Independent Office for Police
OL,13,FConduct (IOPC) which is investigating
OL,14,Fthe allegation.
OL,16,FA spokesperson for the police watchdog
OL,17,Fsaid: "We can confirm we are
OL,18,Finvestigating conduct allegations
OL,19,Fagainst the Chief Constable of
OL,20,FGloucestershire Constabulary, Rod
OL,21,FHansen.
