OL,3,CGloucestershire Chief Constable
OL,4,Csuspended following alleged misconduct
OL,6,F"The investigation follows a referral
OL,7,Fin August from the Office of the
OL,8,FPolice and Crime Commissioner for
OL,9,FGloucestershire.
OL,11,F"The investigation concerns his
OL,12,Fhandling of an allegation against a
OL,13,Fmember of staff, and whether relevant
OL,14,Fpolicies and procedures were
OL,15,Fsubsequently followed.
OL,17,F"We have today (Monday 7 October)
OL,18,Fserved a gross misconduct notice on
OL,19,Fthe Chief Constable to advise him his
OL,20,Fconduct is subject to investigation.
