OL,11,FHe said: "Earlier today, the
OL,12,FIndependent Office of Police Conduct
OL,13,F(IOPC) informed Chief Constable Rod
OL,14,FHansen that it is investigating an
OL,15,Falleged breach of standards of
OL,16,Fprofessional behaviour.
OL,18,F"I have decided to suspend Mr Hansen
OL,19,Ffrom his role with Gloucestershire
OL,20,FConstabulary pending the outcome of
OL,21,Fthis investigation.
