OL,3,CGloucestershire Chief Constable
OL,4,Csuspended following alleged misconduct
OL,6,F"I will emphasise that the decision to
OL,7,Fsuspend is a neutral act. It has no
OL,8,Fbearing on any indication of guilt and
OL,9,Fshould not be seen as such.
OL,11,F"I have spoken to His Majesty's Chief
OL,12,FInspector of Constabulary, Andy Cooke,
OL,13,Fafter taking this decision.
OL,15,F"The Constabulary's Executive Board
OL,16,Fwill provide continuity for the
OL,17,Forganisation.
