OL,3,CGloucestershire Chief Constable
OL,4,Csuspended following alleged misconduct
OL,6,F"My team and I are now working with
OL,7,Fother colleagues in policing to
OL,8,Fnationally identify a temporary Chief
OL,9,FConstable who can lead Gloucestershire
OL,10,FConstabulary during this period.
OL,12,F"I know that this will come as a shock
OL,13,Fto many in the County, especially to
OL,14,Four hard working officers and staff,
OL,15,Fand to our partner organisations, but
OL,16,Fit is right that any allegations are
OL,17,Fdealt with consistently and
OL,18,Finvestigated properly, thoroughly and
OL,19,Fswiftly. I have every confidence that
OL,20,Fthe IOPC will do exactly that.
