OL,6,F"It will be up to the IOPC to lead on
OL,7,Fany communication about the
OL,8,Finvestigation that it considers
OL,9,Fnecessary.
OL,11,F"In the meantime, I would like to
OL,12,Fassure residents and criminals alike
OL,13,Fthat the Constabulary will be
OL,14,Foperating as normal, keeping our
OL,15,Fresidents safe, and preventing and
OL,16,Fdetecting crime."
